msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install.rst:38
msgid ""
"You must have GnuPG installed to verify signatures. For macOS you "
"probably want `GPGTools <https://gpgtools.org/>`_, and for Windows you "
"probably want `Gpg4win <https://www.gpg4win.org/>`_."
msgstr ""

